data.title: Grand Duchess Olga Feodorovna (1839
data.meta_description: Photograph of Grand Duchess Olga Feodorovna. She is standing looking slightly left with her left arm resting on the high wooden table beside her to the right. She is wearing a jacket with a lace blouse and a belt and a number of items of jewellery including a pearl necklace. In her left hand she is holding a folded fan and there is a book on the table. Grand Duchess Olga Feodorovna was the wife of Grand Duke Michael Nikolaevich, the youngest son of Nicholas I, Emperor of Russia. They had seven children.
